{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775884013161,"sessionID":"ses_28510e762ffeZGYsWDSVWsV5pr","part":{"id":"prt_d7aef8e670018759GdAgtrMykl","messageID":"msg_d7aef7f65001ePlnLia5k99gRt","sessionID":"ses_28510e762ffeZGYsWDSVWsV5pr","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884142180,"sessionID":"ses_28510e762ffeZGYsWDSVWsV5pr","part":{"id":"prt_d7af185eb001KXX0GHGqSRfZ6H","messageID":"msg_d7aef7f65001ePlnLia5k99gRt","sessionID":"ses_28510e762ffeZGYsWDSVWsV5pr","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-fd11a50fabc4421fa6cd7ac0c0addd1e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md","content":"# AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values |\n| Module | `manifests` |\n| Language | YAML |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Chart Foundation (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` with chart metadata\n  - Purpose: Define chart name, version, appVersion, and metadata\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm lint manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\"`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Create `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` with default configuration\n  - Purpose: Define default values for all configurable parameters\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm lint manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\"`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Create `manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl` with named templates\n  - Purpose: Define helper templates for name, fullname, labels, selectorLabels, image\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"app.kubernetes.io/name\"`\n\n### Phase 2: WorkloadManager Templates (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Create `workloadmanager.yaml` Deployment template\n  - Purpose: Define WorkloadManager Deployment with configurable replicas, image, resources\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"kind: Deployment\" | head -1`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Implement WorkloadManager Deployment container ports configuration\n  - Purpose: Configure container port from `workloadmanager.service.port`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set workloadmanager.service.port=9090 | grep \"containerPort: 9090\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3**: Implement WorkloadManager Deployment environment variables\n  - Purpose: Inject AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE, REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD from values\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"redis.test:6379\" --set redis.password=\"secret\" | grep \"REDIS_ADDR\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.4**: Implement WorkloadManager Deployment resources configuration\n  - Purpose: Configure CPU/memory limits and requests from `workloadmanager.resources`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set workloadmanager.resources.limits.cpu=1 | grep \"cpu: 1\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.5**: Implement WorkloadManager Deployment health probes\n  - Purpose: Add livenessProbe and readinessProbe for /health endpoint\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"livenessProbe\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.6**: Implement WorkloadManager Deployment extraEnv support\n  - Purpose: Allow additional environment variables via `workloadmanager.extraEnv`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"TEST\",\"value\":\"val\"}]' | grep \"name: TEST\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.7**: Create WorkloadManager Service template\n  - Purpose: Define ClusterIP Service for WorkloadManager\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"kind: Service\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.8**: Implement WorkloadManager Service port configuration\n  - Purpose: Configure service port from `workloadmanager.service.port`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set workloadmanager.service.port=9090 | grep \"port: 9090\"`\n\n### Phase 3: Router Templates (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Create `agentcube-router.yaml` Deployment template\n  - Purpose: Define Router Deployment with configurable replicas, image, resources\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"name: agentcube-router\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: Implement Router Deployment container ports configuration\n  - Purpose: Configure container port from `router.service.targetPort`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set router.service.targetPort=9090 | grep \"containerPort: 9090\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3**: Implement Router Deployment environment variables\n  - Purpose: Inject AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE, REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD, WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"redis.test:6379\" --namespace test | grep \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4**: Implement Router Deployment resources configuration\n  - Purpose: Configure CPU/memory limits and requests from `router.resources`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set router.resources.limits.memory=1Gi | grep \"memory: 1Gi\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.5**: Implement Router Deployment health probes\n  - Purpose: Add livenessProbe (/health/live) and readinessProbe (/health/ready)\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"path: /health/live\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.6**: Implement Router Deployment serviceAccountName support\n  - Purpose: Allow custom ServiceAccount via `router.serviceAccountName`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set router.serviceAccountName=test-sa | grep \"serviceAccountName: test-sa\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.7**: Implement Router Deployment extraEnv support\n  - Purpose: Allow additional environment variables via `router.extraEnv`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"DEBUG\",\"value\":\"true\"}]' | grep \"name: DEBUG\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.8**: Create Router Service template\n  - Purpose: Define ClusterIP Service for Router\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep -A5 \"name: agentcube-router\" | grep \"kind: Service\"`\n\n- [ ] **T3.9**: Implement Router Service port configuration\n  - Purpose: Configure service port and targetPort from values\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set router.service.port=80 | grep \"port: 80\"`\n\n### Phase 4: RBAC Templates (ST-4)\n\n- [ ] **T4.1**: Create `templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` ServiceAccount\n  - Purpose: Define ServiceAccount for WorkloadManager (cluster-scoped)\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"kind: ServiceAccount\"`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2**: Create WorkloadManager ClusterRole with full permissions\n  - Purpose: Define ClusterRole with permissions for agents.x-k8s.io, runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh, pods, secrets\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"kind: ClusterRole\"`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3**: Create WorkloadManager ClusterRoleBinding\n  - Purpose: Bind ClusterRole to ServiceAccount\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" | grep \"kind: ClusterRoleBinding\"`\n\n- [ ] **T4.4**: Create `templates/rbac-router.yaml` with conditional rendering\n  - Purpose: Define Router RBAC (ServiceAccount, Role, RoleBinding) when `router.rbac.create=true`\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set router.rbac.create=true --set router.serviceAccountName=router-sa | grep \"kind: Role\"`\n\n- [ ] **T4.5**: Implement Router Role with secrets permissions\n  - Purpose: Define namespace-scoped Role with secrets permissions\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set router.rbac.create=true | grep \"apiGroups:.*core\"`\n\n### Phase 5: Volcano Scheduler Templates