addr=\"test:6379\" --set-json 'workloadmanager.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"CUSTOM\",\"value\":\"test\"}]' | grep \"name: CUSTOM\"`\n\n- [ ] **T8.8**: Test extraEnv injection for Router\n  - Purpose: Verify extra environment variables are rendered\n  - File: `manifests/charts/base/`\n  - Verification: `helm template agentcube manifests/charts/base --set redis.addr=\"test:6379\" --set-json 'router.extraEnv=[{\"name\":\"LOG_LEVEL\",\"value\":\"debug\"}]' | grep \"name: LOG_LEVEL\"`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nPhase 1 (Foundation) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.1 (Chart.yaml) ──┬── T1.2 (values.yaml)\n                   └── T1.3 (_helpers.tpl)\n                              ├── T2.1 (workloadmanager Deployment)\n                              ├── T3.1 (router Deployment)\n                              ├── T4.1-T4.5 (RBAC templates)\n                              └── T5.1-T5.3 (Volcano scheduler)\n                              └── T7.1 (validation)\n\nPhase 2 (WorkloadManager) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT2.1 ──┬── T2.2 (container ports)\n       ├── T2.3 (env vars)\n       ├── T2.4 (resources)\n       ├── T2.5 (health probes)\n       ├── T2.6 (extraEnv)\n       └── T2.7-T2.8 (Service)\n\nPhase 3 (Router) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT3.1 ──┬── T3.2 (container ports)\n       ├── T3.3 (env vars)\n       ├── T3.4 (resources)\n       ├── T3.5 (health probes)\n       ├── T3.6 (serviceAccountName)\n       ├── T3.7 (extraEnv)\n       └── T3.8-T3.9 (Service)\n\nPhase 4 (RBAC) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.3 ──┬── T4.1 (WorkloadManager SA)\n       ├── T4.2 (ClusterRole)\n       ├── T4.3 (ClusterRoleBinding)\n       └── T4.4-T4.5 (Router RBAC - conditional)\n\nPhase 5 (Volcano Scheduler) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nT1.3 ──┬── T5.1 (conditional rendering)\n       ├── T5.2 (Deployment)\n       └── T5.3 (RBAC)