uter.yaml` | Create | ~100 | Router Deployment + Service |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` | Create | ~80 | WorkloadManager RBAC (SA, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding) |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml` | Create | ~50 | Router RBAC (conditional) |\n| `manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` | Create | ~60 | Volcano scheduler (conditional) |\n| `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` | Create | ~150 | AgentRuntime CRD |\n| `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` | Create | ~150 | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Chart.yaml Structure\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nname: agentcube\ndescription: A Helm chart for AgentCube\ntype: application\nversion: 0.1.0\nappVersion: 1.0.0\nkeywords:\n  - agentcube\n  - kubernetes\n  - sandbox\n  - ai-agents\nmaintainers:\n  - name: volcano-sh\n    email: volcano-sh@example.com\nsources:\n  - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n```\n\n### _helpers.tpl Named Templates\n\n```yaml\n{{- define \"agentcube.name\" -}}\n{{- default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- end -}}\n\n{{- define \"agentcube.fullname\" -}}\n{{- if .Values.fullnameOverride -}}\n{{- .Values.fullnameOverride | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- else -}}\n{{- $name := default .Chart.Name .Values.nameOverride -}}\n{{- if contains $name .Release.Name -}}\n{{- .Release.Name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- else -}}\n{{- printf \"%s-%s\" .Release.Name $name | trunc 63 | trimSuffix \"-\" -}}\n{{- end -}}\n{{- end -}}\n{{- end -}}\n\n{{- define \"agentcube.labels\" -}}\napp.kubernetes.io/name: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\napp.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\napp.kubernetes.io/version: {{ .Chart.AppVersion }}\napp.kubernetes.io/managed-by: {{ .Release.Service }}\n{{- end -}}\n\n{{- define \"agentcube.selectorLabels\" -}}\napp: {{ include \"agentcube.name\" . }}\n{{- end -}}\n```\n\n### Required Value Validation Pattern\n\n```yaml\n{{- if not .Values.redis.addr }}\n{{- fail \"redis.addr must be provided\" }}\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n### Conditional RBAC Rendering Pattern\n\n```yaml\n{{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}\n{{- if not .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n{{- fail \"router.serviceAccountName must be set when router.rbac.create is true\" }}\n{{- end }}\n# RBAC resources...\n{{- end }}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Foundation | T1.1-T1.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: WorkloadManager | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Router | T3.1-T3.9 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: RBAC | T4.1-T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Volcano Scheduler | T5.1-T5.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: CRDs | T6.1-T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Validation | T7.1-T7.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Tests | T8.1-T8.8 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/47 tasks)**\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `changes/AR-030/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\n- Proposal: `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`\n- deployment/design.md — Reference implementation details\n- ci-cd/design.md — E2E Helm usage patterns\n- Helm 3 Documentation — Chart structure, templates, values best practices\n- Kubernetes API Reference — Deployment, Service, RBAC schemas"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775884142140,"end":1775884142176}}}}
